{"id":"v002_ch001_s009","versionId":"version_002","chapterId":"ch001","chapterNumber":1,"chapterTitle":"甄士隐梦幻识通灵 贾雨村风尘怀闺秀","sentenceIndex":9,"paragraphIndex":3,"text":"我之罪固不免，然闺阁中本自历历有人，万不可因我之不肖，自护己短，一并使其泯灭也。","punctuation":"。","metadata":{"hasVariant":false,"hasAnnotation":true,"wordCount":42}}
